# llamars

A Rust wrapper for the llama.cpp library, providing safe and ergonomic bindings for running LLaMA models in Rust applications.

## Features (WIP!!)

- **Safe Rust API** - Memory-safe wrappers around llama.cpp functionality
- **High Performance** - Direct bindings to optimized C++ implementation
- **Easy to Use** - Builder pattern for configuration and simple API design
- **Chat Support** - Built-in conversation management and chat templates
- **Interactive Mode** - Ready-to-use interactive chat interface
- **Flexible** - Support for various model formats and configurations
- **Cross Platform** - Works on Linux, macOS, and Windows
- **GPU Acceleration** - CUDA, Metal, and OpenCL support

